{"tid":499691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★香港IT狗正式玩完！政府明年推行特快入境計劃，吸引IT人才","createTime":"2017-12-15T06:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T02:06:44.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0bb0c6a9e14f7e9e8bf5c19da7c424af85adbf13","tid":499691,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:01:19.000Z","msg":"政府公布智慧城市藍圖，利用創新及科技改善市民生活，增強香港吸引力。<br />\n<br />\n包括明年<span style=\"color: red;\">推行特快入境計劃</span>，吸引及挽留創科優秀人才，特別在生物科技、數據科學、人工智能等方面；亦將開發「快速支付系統」，用戶可隨時以電子方式支付。<br />\n<br />\n明年亦推出十億元資助計劃，協助安老及康復服務機構試用及購置科技產品。<br />\n<br />\n在二零二零年，會為巿民提供免費數碼個人身份，以單一身份認證，進行政府及商業的網上交易。<br />\n<br />\n在環境方面，將使用遙測感應裝置，監察街道和公眾地方的清潔、廢屑箱和回收桶使用情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5a334e49e60383683e81f267/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5a334e49e60383683e81f267%2F&d=TNOiLsxCBh2L6hAYJQdfLozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=70a4c5bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5a334e49e60383683e81f267/</a>"},{"pid":"4d2b504a6a386ffbc6535e26c18b4a2eec65748f","tid":499691,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:01:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2c525e146a44aa309f65042eb72941f7c35ab1","tid":499691,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:01:57.000Z","msg":"推行特快入境計劃<br />\n推行特快入境計劃<br />\n推行特快入境計劃<br />\n推行特快入境計劃"},{"pid":"4345b119718a5ff9c9e1ff59c06fc274ee227b3b","tid":499691,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T06:04:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">吸引及挽留創科優秀人才</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsample<br />\n<img src=\"https://www1.picturepush.com/photo/a/8133409/640/8133409.jpg\" data-th